### Target Specific Deployment with vercel curl

Source: https://github.com/vercel/vercel/blob/main/packages/cli/src/commands/curl/README.md

Use the --deployment flag to test a specific deployment by ID. Accepts deployment IDs with or without the 'dpl_' prefix, which is automatically added if omitted.

```bash
# Test a specific deployment by ID
vercel curl /api/status --deployment ERiL45NJvP8ghWxgbvCM447bmxwV

# Or with the dpl_ prefix
vercel curl /api/status --deployment dpl_ERiL45NJvP8ghWxgbvCM447bmxwV
```

