### List deployment events (JavaScript)

Source: https://github.com/vercel/vercel/blob/main/packages/client/README.md

Canonical list of events emitted by createDeployment for tracking file and deployment lifecycle stages. This list can be used to filter or react to specific events (e.g., 'ready' or 'error'). Note: the example uses JavaScript array syntax with comments and is intended for reference in code.

```JavaScript
[
  // File events
  'hashes-calculated',
  'file-count',
  'file-uploaded',
  'all-files-uploaded',
  // Deployment events
  'created',
  'building',
  'ready',
  'alias-assigned',
  'warning',
  'error',
];
```

